QueryToExecute:
select
  access_point_arn as resource,
  case
    when posix_user is null then 'alarm'
    else 'ok'
  end as status,
  case
    when posix_user is null then title || ' does not enforce a user identity.'
    else title || ' enforces a user identity.'
  end as reason
  
  , region, account_id
from
  aws_efs_access_point;
